                <b>Step 3 : Weight loss goal</b>
                <form action="/weight-loss-rate" method="POST">
                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                        <strong>Message:</strong><br> According to the collected data your BMI is: __,_. The healthy body weight range that corresponds to your height is ____ - ____ kg.
                    </div> <br>
                    <label for="weightGoal">What is your target body weight?</label>
                    <input type="number" id="weightGoal" name="weight-goal"><br><br>

                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                        <strong>Message:</strong><br> The recommended weight loss rate is between 2-4 kg per month or 0.5-1 kg per week. Nevertheless, keep in mind that by reducing your initial body weight by 5-10% you will achieve substantial benefits in terms of health, quality of life and disease prevention.
                    </div> <br>
                    <label for="weightRate">How many kilograms you wish to lose on a monthly basis?</label>
                    <input type="number" id="weightRate" name="weight-rate"><br><br><br>
                    <input type="submit" id="submitData" name="sumbit-data" value="Next">
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
